Fast Healing
	KEY:Fast Healing ~ Razor Boar
	SOURCEPAGE:p.221
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:A razor boar regains lost hit points at the rate of 10 per round. Fast healing does not restore hit points lost from starvation, thirst, or suffocation, and it does not allow the razor boar to regrow or reattach lost body parts.

Scent
	KEY:Scent ~ Razor Boar
	SOURCEPAGE:p.221
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:RazorBoarRaceAbility.RaceAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:A razor boar can detect approaching enemies, sniff out hidden foes, and track by sense of smell.



